t a=C2=A0<em>definition=C2=A0</em>of market manipulation =E2=80=94=C2=A0it =
is not illegal to do irrational trades =E2=80=94=C2=A0but it is a rough gui=
de to=C2=A0<em>recognizing=C2=A0</em>market manipulation.=C2=A0</p><p style=
=3D"margin: 16px 0;">On the other hand he didn=E2=80=99t do this in the sto=
